Hey, Elma? Were there always this many indigens
kicking around here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0002
rows.name:
No, definitely not.
I wonder if the plant is drawing them somehow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0005
rows.name: We may have finished the data collection...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0006
rows.name: But it looks like the mission isn't over just yet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0008
rows.name: Yeah. They may be dealing with the same problem.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0009
rows.name: Bring on nasty critters! Friends will teach them all a lesson![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085603_MSG0010
rows.name: You can help out anytime, ya know.[ST:wait ]
